Practical Peripherals Frequently Asked Questions
Compiled by Dan Birchall (birchall@pilot.njin.net)
Revision 1.05, August 16, 1994

This document contains answers to frequently asked questions about PPI
(Practical Peripherals, Inc.) products.  This information was compiled
from various sources including PPI's catalog and information services.
Please send comments, questions, and corrections for this FAQ document 
FAQ to: birchall@pilot.njin.net

This file should NOT be considered official PPI documentation.  Prices
listed below are suggested list prices, and discount retail prices are
generally substantially lower.  Many thanks to the PPIforum staffers -
Yvonne, Dan, Gene, Brian and Paul - who provide information and online
help to many users and also provide accurate data for this document.


