What ProClass modems does PPI offer for business and specialized use?

ProClass modems feature advanced functions including synchronous mode,
leased line capabilities, caller ID, Hayes Autosync, on-line help, and 
line testing routines, along with all the features of the counterparts
in the Practical line.  Quicklink II/Fax and WinFax Lite are included.
The ProClass PC288SA modem supports DTE speeds of 230.4kbps, when used
with the PC-HSSP card.  The PC-HSSP features a coprocessor and dual 1k
caches, and also emulates a 16550 UART.

